<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
{#
  Access Review escalation notification email.
  Context variables (all required):
    campaign           AccessReviewCampaign
    escalatedItems     AccessReviewItem[]
    escalatingReviewer User
    count              int
  ISO 27001 A.5.18 — audit evidence for escalated recertification items.
#}
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #1e1b4b; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0284c7 0%, #7c3aed 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; margin: 0; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
        .label { font-weight: bold; color: #374151; }
        .escalated-box { background: #fefce8; border: 1px solid #f59e0b; padding: 12px; margin: 16px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin-top: 12px; }
        th, td { border: 1px solid #d1d5db; padding: 8px 10px; text-align: left; font-size: 0.9em; }
        th { background-color: #1e3a5f; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; }
        code { background: #f3f4f6; padding: 2px 5px; border-radius: 3px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.85em; }
        .footer { text-align: center; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 11px; padding: 16px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin-top: 8px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h2 style="margin:0; font-size:1.2em;">&#9888; UAR Escalation: {{ count }} Item(s) Require Your Review</h2>
        <p style="margin:6px 0 0; opacity:0.85; font-size:0.9em;">User Access Recertification — ISO 27001 A.5.18</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>One or more access review items have been <strong>escalated</strong> and require a decision from a CISO or Manager.</p>

        <div class="escalated-box">
            <p class="label" style="margin:0 0 6px;">Campaign Details</p>
            <table style="border:none; width:auto;">
                <tr>
                    <td style="border:none; padding:3px 12px 3px 0; font-weight:bold; color:#374151;">Campaign</td>
                    <td style="border:none; padding:3px 0;">{{ campaign.name|e }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="border:none; padding:3px 12px 3px 0; font-weight:bold; color:#374151;">Due Date</td>
                    <td style="border:none; padding:3px 0;">{{ campaign.dueDate ? campaign.dueDate|date('Y-m-d') : '–' }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="border:none; padding:3px 12px 3px 0; font-weight:bold; color:#374151;">{{ 'access_review.field.decided_by'|trans({}, 'access_review') }}</td>
                    <td style="border:none; padding:3px 0;">{{ escalatingReviewer.email|e }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="border:none; padding:3px 12px 3px 0; font-weight:bold; color:#374151;">Items escalated</td>
                    <td style="border:none; padding:3px 0;">{{ count }}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <p class="label">Escalated Items</p>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Subject User</th>
                    <th>Email</th>
                    <th>Reviewed Role</th>
                    <th>{{ 'access_review.field.decided_by'|trans({}, 'access_review') }}</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {% for item in escalatedItems %}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{ item.subjectUser ? item.subjectUser.fullName|e : '–' }}</td>
                    <td>{{ item.subjectUser ? item.subjectUser.email|e : '–' }}</td>
                    <td><code>{{ item.reviewedRole|e }}</code></td>
                    <td>{{ item.decidedBy ? item.decidedBy.email|e : '–' }}</td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <p style="margin-top:16px;">{{ 'access_review.escalation.notify_cta'|trans({}, 'access_review') }}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        ISO 27001 A.5.18 / A.8.2 &middot; NIS2 Art. 21(2)(e) &middot; BSI ORP.4
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
